---
const technologies = [
  { name: 'Java',       category: 'lang' },
  { name: 'TypeScript', category: 'lang' },
  { name: 'Dart',       category: 'lang' },
  { name: 'React',      category: 'web' },
  { name: 'Astro',      category: 'web' },
  { name: 'Tailwind',   category: 'web' },
  { name: 'Node.js',    category: 'back' },
  { name: 'Express',    category: 'back' },
  { name: 'SQLite',     category: 'data' },
  { name: 'Flutter',    category: 'mobile' },
  { name: 'JavaFX',     category: 'desktop' },
  { name: 'Git',        category: 'tool' },
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-12 fade-in">
      <span class="font-mono text-sm text-[#4F8BFF]">0x01</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#F2F2F0]">
        <span data-lang="es">Sobre m&iacute;</span>
        <span data-lang="en">About me</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr] gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="fade-in space-y-4 text-base text-[#F2F2F0] leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          <span data-lang="es">Tengo 22 a&ntilde;os y me acabo de graduar de Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma en Alicante. Empec&eacute; con curiosidad por entender c&oacute;mo funcionaban las cosas que us&aacute;bamos a diario y termin&eacute; metido en c&oacute;digo a tiempo completo.</span>
          <span data-lang="en">I'm 22 and I've just graduated in Multiplatform Application Development (DAM) in Alicante. I started out curious about how the things we used every day worked, and ended up fully into code.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#7A7A80]">
          <span data-lang="es">Lo que m&aacute;s disfruto es montar funcionalidades de extremo a extremo, del esquema de base de datos a la pantalla que ve el usuario. Me gusta dejar el c&oacute;digo entendible para quien venga despu&eacute;s y discutir decisiones t&eacute;cnicas.</span>
          <span data-lang="en">What I enjoy most is building features end to end &mdash; from the database schema to the screen the user sees. I like leaving code readable for whoever comes next and discussing technical decisions.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#7A7A80]">
          <span data-lang="es">Busco mi primer trabajo en desarrollo. Actualmente tengo poca experiencia profesional, de igual manera, aqui muestro cuatro proyectos terminados que cubren web fullstack, datos, m&oacute;vil, escritorio y el portfolio que est&aacute;s viendo.</span>
          <span data-lang="en">I'm looking for my first developer job. I have little professional experience yet, but I'm showcasing four finished projects covering fullstack web, data, mobile, desktop &mdash; plus this portfolio.</span>
        </p>

        <div class="pt-4 mt-4 border-t border-[#1F1F23] flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-1 font-mono text-xs text-[#7A7A80]">
          <span>
            <span class="text-[#4F8BFF]/70">
              <span data-lang="es">disponibilidad:</span><span data-lang="en">availability:</span>
            </span>
            <span data-lang="es">inmediata</span><span data-lang="en">immediate</span>
          </span>
          <span>
            <span class="text-[#4F8BFF]/70">
              <span data-lang="es">modalidad:</span><span data-lang="en">mode:</span>
            </span>
            <span data-lang="es">presencial / remoto / h&iacute;brido</span>
            <span data-lang="en">on-site / remote / hybrid</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-[#7A7A80] mb-5 tracking-wide">
          <span class="text-[#4F8BFF]/70">$</span> ls ~/stack
        </p>
        <div class="border border-[#1F1F23] bg-[#131316]">
          {technologies.map((tech, i) => (
            <div class={`flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-[#1F1F23]/40 transition-colors duration-150 ${i !== technologies.length - 1 ? 'border-b border-[#1F1F23]' : ''}`}>
              <span class="text-[#F2F2F0]">{tech.name}</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[#7A7A80]">{tech.category}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
